1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:37,800
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:40,520
(Office)

4
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:40,160
(Did she leave Jindian?)

5
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:43,200
(Will I still see her in the future?)

6
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,559
You can't make
all the money in the world,

7
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,469
and there will
always be more work to do.

8
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:54,029
There are also
countless obstacles in real life.

9
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:56,390
However, life is short.

10
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:58,510
In this fleeting life,

11
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,830
love may be

12
00:03:00,070 --> 00:03:01,959
but a momentary bloom.

13
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,509
It might even be
the only one in the vast ocean.

14
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:06,399
If you don't grasp the opportunity,

15
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,320
you will lose it forever.

16
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,640
(Qingcheng District People's Court,
Tianhai City)

17
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,320
Why didn't you attend court?

18
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,160
To avoid suspicions.

19
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,950
Let's be together.

20
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,760
Let's be together.

21
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,829
Do you know?

22
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:20,880
I've thought about it
for a long time last night.

23
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,470
We listed out all our difficulties

24
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,149
and trapped ourselves inside.

25
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:26,479
But what will happen

26
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,070
in the future,

27
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,800
whether we are together or not,

28
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,800
I've thought about everything
that could happen in the future.

29
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,760
But no matter which possibility it is,
it will only happen in the future.

30
00:04:36,710 --> 00:04:38,070
Besides,

31
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,120
they'll also make me regret.

32
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,590
I just want to cherish the present.

33
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,950
If we put an end to it right now,

34
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,239
every time we meet in the future,

35
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,309
we will have to suppress our feelings

36
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,760
with only regret left.

37
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:55,150
Instead of having that,

38
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:56,829
why not forget everything

39
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,320
and courageously be together?

40
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,630
Perhaps we'd be sick of each other

41
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,360
before the final day.

42
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,629
Then, we can just

43
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:06,880
break up happily.

44
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,320
I've thought about all you just said.

45
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,880
But in that case,

46
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:13,829
there will always be

47
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:15,679
a time bomb that can go off at any time

48
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,200
in our relationship.

49
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,030
It will end at any time.

50
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,070
This isn't fair for you.

51
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,360
Shen Xiezhi!

52
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,320
You were the one who said

53
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,320
you'd take care of me forever.

54
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:33,680
Let's be together.

55
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,710
From now on.

56
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,829
The agreement is in force immediately.

57
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,320
The relationship
will be executed immediately.

58
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,799
I smelled something nice at the door.

59
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,120
It's a feast, as expected.

60
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:08,440
My favorite hotpot.

61
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:10,120
I'm starving.

62
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,679
So many dishes.

63
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,240
What a feast.

64
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,189
Let me grab one.

65
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:16,999
What are you doing?

66
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,479
Wash your hands before you eat.

67
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,320
I washed my hands before I came back.

68
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,590
Go and wash your hands.

69
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,880
What kind of naughty child are you?

70
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,709
Fine, I'll wash.

71
00:06:31,710 --> 00:06:34,270
I've washed my hands now.
Can I eat now?

72
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,879
You are back so soon.

73
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,879
I thought there was a burglary.

74
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,559
Which burglar would treat you so well

75
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,509
by cooking

76
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,950
and making hotpot for you?

77
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,390
Something's really off, then.

78
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,749
You came home early

79
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,240
and made dinner on your own.

80
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:52,950
Did you make a lot of money?

81
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,709
I know.

82
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:57,070
A huge bonus.

83
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,630
I know.

84
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:04,630
He Xiuguang's case is closed, right?

85
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,950
There's one more good thing.

86
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,559
What is it?

87
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,440
Fine. Just tell me. I can't guess it.

88
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:18,800
Shen Xiezhi and I are in a relationship.

89
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,880
Seriously?

90
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,760
Finally?

91
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,880
That deserves a celebration.

92
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,919
I wish you and Shen Xiezhi

93
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,830
could live in harmony
and give birth to a child soon.

94
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,189
What's that?

95
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:37,390
There's nothing wrong with that.

96
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,200
What did you say?

97
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,509
I am in a relationship.

98
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:51,710
Really?

99
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,000
With whom?

100
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,680
Is it related to that gift of yours?

101
00:07:57,560 --> 00:08:00,200
The cat is finally out of the bag now.

102
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,200
Yes. It's her.

103
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,389
I knew it.

104
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:07,240
You can't hide anything from me.

105
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,709
Find one day

106
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:10,510
and bring her back to meet us.

107
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,760
It's still too early.

108
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,629
We just got into a relationship

109
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,189
and you're already
trying to question her.

110
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:21,069
How can you misunderstand me?

111
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,749
I am not a close-minded parent

112
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,880
who is picky about girls.

113
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,559
Also, I won't contact her in private

114
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,749
before you bring her home.

115
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:29,679
Yes.

116
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,320
You must approve of everything.

117
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,509
We just want

118
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:34,830
to find an opportunity
to have a meal together.

119
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,280
Sure.

120
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,830
I'll ask her later.

121
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:42,800
I'll try to get my client's opinion.

122
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,320
That's great.

123
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,440
Go inside.

124
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,070
Go inside.

125
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:59,199
I saw you
coming out of Mr. Guan's office

126
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,710
with a serious expression.

127
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,160
What happened?

128
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,640
Well...

129
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,200
I'm going to tell you, then.

130
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,239
Speak.

131
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,800
I told him

132
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,999
about your plan to usurp the throne.

133
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,590
Enough. Just tell me.

134
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,440
I'm just annoyed.

135
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,749
Mr. Guan is very unhappy.

136
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:23,160
Didn't our team just hire Lawyer Wang?

137
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:24,079
After he joined,

138
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,920
he ruined my case immediately.

139
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,999
He ruined

140
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,789
the sure-win case?

141
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,909
Look.

142
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:30,199
Well,

143
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,959
his results were good in school,

144
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,719
and he was a member
of the students' council.

145
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:36,549
However, he had no experience in society
and didn't know how to adapt.

146
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,849
The lawyer on the opposite

147
00:09:37,850 --> 00:09:40,650
just used a few tricks

148
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,879
and tactics

149
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,959
and made Lawyer Wang fall into the trap.

150
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,750
Yes. This is
the most troublesome thing now.

151
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,680
Why don't we just

152
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:50,280
hire a few more people?

153
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,359
Do you think Ronghe Law Firm

154
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,479
can't hire anyone?

155
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,509
Yes.

156
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,280
We can hire people, indeed.

157
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:57,560
This is exactly what Mr. Guan
was discussing with me just now.

158
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,149
If we have an official recruitment,

159
00:09:59,150 --> 00:09:59,789
our HR department

160
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:00,749
can get a group

161
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:03,160
of so-called ace students
from the best law schools.

162
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,599
But you know

163
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,669
that litigation

164
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:08,400
requires people with talent.

165
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:10,110
Right?

166
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:12,040
Can you think of

167
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,680
any suitable people?

168
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:16,110
Let me think about it.

169
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,160
Please think about it.

170
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,950
Someone came to my mind.

171
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:29,560
Wonderful.

172
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,269
Look.

173
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:32,079
Send her contact to me.

174
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,389
I'll meet her tomorrow morning

175
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:34,789
and treat you to lunch in the afternoon.

176
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,079
Pick any place you want.

177
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,640
I've been saving her for myself.

178
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,839
Here. Hold your cup.

179
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,959
I...

180
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,479
Come on.

181
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,999
I really need this person.

182
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,079
You are a talented person.

183
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,839
I only have talent, but I have no one.

184
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,479
You don't need me.

185
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,719
Your team doesn't need anyone.

186
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,959
Your talent alone is enough.

187
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,350
I need help.

188
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,040
It's hot.

189
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,029
Since both of you
have decided to be together,

190
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:05,999
you should stop overthinking.

191
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:10,110
Your main thing now is
to deal with your work problems.

192
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:11,789
Have you
already considered changing areas?

193
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:14,999
Right now, it seems like changing to
another area is easier for me.

194
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,280
However,

195
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:18,920
I don't know if I can find a job

196
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,479
so suddenly.

197
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,950
I'm sure you can.

198
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,359
You are now an influencer

199
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,629
followed by a major influencer.

200
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:25,879
You'll be fine.

201
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,280
I only

202
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:29,320
feel sorry for Lin.

203
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,199
He finally got me

204
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,230
to work for him here

205
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,920
so he can play sports.

206
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,870
If I resign suddenly,

207
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,400
what will he do?

208
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,909
The institution stays,
but people come and go.

209
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,429
Lin still understands that.

210
00:11:45,430 --> 00:11:46,749
Don't worry about him for nothing.

211
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,199
Just take good care of yourself.

212
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:50,359
He has a car and a house, after all.

213
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,990
He even has an excellent wife.

214
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:55,239
Before his children graduated
from high school, he already bought his house.

215
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,440
What about you?

216
00:11:57,720 --> 00:12:00,029
I don't know how to tell him.

217
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,319
Just tell him

218
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:03,719
your heart has been covered,

219
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:06,110
and you wanted to experience
being the female lead of a love drama.

220
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:08,280
I'd rather say

221
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,959
I've become a famous influencer

222
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,879
and have to leave.

223
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,479
Perhaps he will feel happy for me

224
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,350
and even send me off happily.

225
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,070
Nothing wrong with that.

226
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:21,830
This is amazing.

227
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:27,400
(Unknown Number)

228
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,269
Hello.

229
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,149
Hello.

230
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:37,119
I am Ms. Lou Yue's assistant.

231
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,029
Are you Qin Rui?

232
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,440
Ms. Lou?

233
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:42,319
Yes.

234
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,470
A call from Ronghe Law Firm.

235
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:44,789
Go ahead.

236
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:46,629
Are you free tomorrow?

237
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:48,999
Our partner wants to speak to you.

238
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,110
Me? Yes.

239
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,319
I am free. I can do it.

240
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:54,959
Sure.

241
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,789
Do check your messages later.

242
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,750
We will send you
a text from the law firm.

243
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,029
Thank you.

244
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,830
Thank you so much.

245
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:06,199
Shen Xiezhi brings you good fortune.

246
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,320
Hold on.

247
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,669
Is this for real?

248
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,640
I didn't even
send Ronghe Law Firm my resume.

249
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:13,239
I'm sure you are too excellent

250
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,680
and have been appreciated by Lou Yue.

251
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,560
But the people at Ronghe Law Firm
are still working at this hour.

252
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:18,280
It's too competitive.
Life is stressful over there.

253
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,950
Why are you sighing?

254
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,800
This is good news. Eat.

255
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,200
(Are you asleep?)

256
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:41,070
(Not yet. What is it?)

257
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:44,110
(I'm going to an interview
at Ronghe Law Firm tomorrow.)

258
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,920
(Cheer me up.)

259
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,669
(That's wonderful.)

260
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,280
(That's one of the top-tier law firms.)

261
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,560
(But I don't feel confident.)

262
00:14:02,430 --> 00:14:04,990
(Lawyer Qin gets nervous too?)

263
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:07,669
(What about
that fearless persona of yours)

264
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,719
(that is willing)

265
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:11,560
(to go through anything
for your client?)

266
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:14,520
(I was thinking)

267
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,230
(that if I joined Ronghe Law Firm,)

268
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:20,560
(what would happen if you
got promoted to the High Court.)

269
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,119
(Don't worry.)

270
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,470
(I won't get promoted
to the High Court so soon.)

271
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,470
(Just go to the interview
with peace of mind.)

272
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,199
(Besides,)

273
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,909
(Didn't we agree)

274
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,549
(to focus on the present
during the day?)

275
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:36,040
(We'll talk about what happens
in the future.)

276
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,230
(Are you swamped by love?)

277
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,110
(Do your best.)

278
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,160
(Rest well tonight)

279
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:44,200
(and calmly face
what's to come tomorrow.)

280
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,920
(All right. Got it.)

281
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:57,080
(Marriage Legal Counsel)

282
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,239
(I'm probably the one)

283
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,800
(who is swamped by love.)

284
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:23,919
♪Turn around for every part of life♪

285
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:28,140
♪Rushing between buildings♪

286
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:32,320
♪Caught in the grind of daily living♪

287
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:35,960
♪Facing the surging waves of life♪

288
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:36,680
Hello.

289
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:39,560
Is this Mingding Building?

290
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,560
This is it.

291
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:41,160
Thank you.

292
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:41,760
You're welcome.

293
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:45,629
♪Ready to chase dreams
through sleepless nights♪

294
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:52,680
♪For the distant place we long to reach♪

295
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:53,880
Let's go over them again.

296
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:57,000
Here. Here, too.

297
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,520
(Ronghe Law Firm)

298
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:00,520
Get to work first.

299
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,480
Hello.

300
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:04,760
You must be Qin Rui.

301
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:06,240
Yes. I'm here for an interview.

302
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,040
This way.

303
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,000
Thank you.

304
00:16:08,230 --> 00:16:10,809
♪Even if the road
beneath my feet is winding♪

305
00:16:10,810 --> 00:16:13,140
♪I still look ahead with hope♪

306
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:16,960
♪I will run toward the future♪

307
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:21,319
♪Sweeping away the dust between us♪

308
00:16:21,319 --> 00:16:22,560
(Lou Yue, Senior Partner)

309
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:23,959
(Ronghe Law Firm)
Mr. Lao.

310
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,999
Wansheng Group's diligence report
for this year is done.

311
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:29,079
A dozen of our people
worked on it for half a month.

312
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,200
Shouldn't you reward us?

313
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:36,590
Yamei Holding Group rewarded our team
with a Northern Lights Europe trip last year.

314
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,029
This year,

315
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,520
try to arrange something.

316
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:42,800
Come in.

317
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,070
Sure. I have an interview here.

318
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,640
Let's talk later.

319
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:47,909
Sure.

320
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:48,990
I'm hanging up.

321
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:52,710
Ms. Lou.

322
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,230
Come in.

323
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,149
Sit.

324
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:58,230
I didn't expect to meet you again.

325
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,160
Yes.

326
00:17:00,382 --> 00:17:01,719
I didn't expect us

327
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,280
to be fated.

328
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,709
What do you think?

329
00:17:04,710 --> 00:17:06,160
Are you a little surprised?

330
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:08,750
I personally asked for you.

331
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:11,260
Previously, in an internal meeting,

332
00:17:11,261 --> 00:17:12,669
someone used Rui's Legal Lens

333
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:14,310
to explain his points.

334
00:17:14,390 --> 00:17:16,359
A few senior lawyers and I

335
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:17,629
found it interesting

336
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:19,200
and followed your account.

337
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,359
Ms. Lou, thank you for your appreciation.

338
00:17:21,360 --> 00:17:23,920
I remember you had a case

339
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:26,149
called "The Kind Teeth".

340
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:27,200
Yes.

341
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:29,149
This is a good title.

342
00:17:29,150 --> 00:17:30,759
It helps instill legal awareness

343
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,160
with a clear line of thinking.

344
00:17:32,197 --> 00:17:33,847
It also shows a solid grasp of the law.

345
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:37,279
In this era,

346
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:38,559
lawyers

347
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:39,709
can no longer

348
00:17:39,710 --> 00:17:42,310
study laws and cases in a strict manner.

349
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:44,680
They still need to know
what the public is thinking.

350
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,189
So, I asked my assistant

351
00:17:46,190 --> 00:17:47,470
to call you.

352
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:50,989
So,

353
00:17:50,990 --> 00:17:52,470
what do you think?

354
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:55,550
It still feels like a dream to me.

355
00:17:56,390 --> 00:17:57,510
All right.

356
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,839
I want you as my assistant lawyer.

357
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,200
You'll work under me from now on.

358
00:18:03,670 --> 00:18:04,119
Oh.

359
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:06,039
The other lawyers

360
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:07,119
I told you just now

361
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:08,879
also have a strong foundation.

362
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,229
That's what you are lacking.

363
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:11,710
You need to catch up soon.

364
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,389
Don't worry, Ms. Lou.

365
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:15,039
I will surely work hard

366
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,039
and not disappoint you.

367
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,360
Do your best.

368
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:36,360
(Lian Yongjiu's Interview)

369
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:45,030
Ms. Jing.

370
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:47,990
What's wrong, Ms. Jing?

371
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:51,030
You don't look too happy today.

372
00:18:53,230 --> 00:18:55,550
How did your husband's interview go?

373
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,799
Don't mention it.

374
00:18:57,800 --> 00:18:59,839
He rejected the job on the phone.

375
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,389
HR required him to travel
on a business trip.

376
00:19:01,390 --> 00:19:03,119
Don't you think he's stubborn?

377
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:05,360
If he goes on a business trip,
I can take care of the children.

378
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:07,359
Otherwise, we can still find a nanny.

379
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:08,879
But he just rejected the job.

380
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,229
Exactly.

381
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:11,799
Xiao Bing and I are also around.

382
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:12,319
Besides,

383
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:14,669
my in-laws
also have nothing to do at home.

384
00:19:14,670 --> 00:19:15,990
Seriously.

385
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:22,270
Should I call Fan and ask him again?

386
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,469
Is that fine?

387
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:25,839
What about it? Let's ask him.

388
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:27,230
What if it's possible?

389
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,200
It's Fan.

390
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:31,940
Hello.

391
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:33,310
Fan.

392
00:19:33,360 --> 00:19:34,039
What a coincidence.

393
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,599
I was just about to call you

394
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:36,989
and you called me first.

395
00:19:36,990 --> 00:19:37,759
Is this

396
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:39,759
about Lian?

397
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:40,990
It is.

398
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,640
Really?

399
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:45,669
Fan,

400
00:19:45,670 --> 00:19:46,149
I want

401
00:19:46,150 --> 00:19:48,279
to explain this to you.

402
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:52,039
Mr. Lian was worried that no one
would take care of his children

403
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:54,360
when he was out on a business trip.

404
00:19:54,670 --> 00:19:55,469
You should know

405
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:57,429
that his wife is our deputy chief judge.

406
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:59,990
She's also very busy.

407
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:02,429
He was afraid

408
00:20:02,430 --> 00:20:03,839
that he would be wasting your time,

409
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:05,470
so he rejected the offer.

410
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:08,080
This is all negotiable.

411
00:20:08,150 --> 00:20:09,909
He is the project manager

412
00:20:09,910 --> 00:20:11,920
so he doesn't have to be
on the frontline all the time.

413
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:12,839
He can arrange

414
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,470
most of his business trips.

415
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,840
Does it mean he still has a chance?

416
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:19,039
Absolutely.

417
00:20:19,040 --> 00:20:20,229
Give me his phone number.

418
00:20:20,230 --> 00:20:21,880
Let me contact him directly.

419
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:22,559
Sure.

420
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:24,319
Let me share your WeChat contacts

421
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:26,189
to each other.

422
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:27,599
I'll also send you his number.

423
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:29,629
I still have a meeting to attend.
Talk to you later.

424
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:31,189
Sure. Talk to you later.

425
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:32,470
Thank you.

426
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:37,559
Done.

427
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:39,680
He is really lucky.

428
00:20:39,910 --> 00:20:41,950
What do you mean by lucky?

429
00:20:42,324 --> 00:20:44,440
He has a good reputation.

430
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:46,080
Everyone knows about it.

431
00:20:46,230 --> 00:20:47,709
It's still thanks to you.

432
00:20:47,710 --> 00:20:49,440
It has nothing to do with me.

433
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:51,030
Anyway, thank you.

434
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,640
Enough with the courtesy.

435
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,160
I won't accept it.

436
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,120
I'll take your pawn.

437
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:02,950
Let's see your next move.

438
00:21:03,430 --> 00:21:04,840
This is bad.

439
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:10,200
Hello. Welcome.

440
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,510
She's looking for you.

441
00:21:17,470 --> 00:21:18,799
What are you pulling?

442
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,189
Are you breaking my momentum?

443
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:21,990
Probably about
your retirement insurance.

444
00:21:25,190 --> 00:21:26,470
Why are you here?

445
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:30,400
- Let us speak for a moment.
- Sure.

446
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:32,080
Come and sit here.

447
00:21:34,470 --> 00:21:35,429
What is it?

448
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:36,990
Why have you come here to find me?

449
00:21:40,390 --> 00:21:41,359
Director.

450
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:42,680
Director?

451
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:45,790
Why do I have a bad feeling about this?

452
00:21:45,910 --> 00:21:47,230
Did something happen at the law firm?

453
00:21:48,710 --> 00:21:50,229
Nothing can happen at the law firm.

454
00:21:50,230 --> 00:21:51,790
Besides splitting the profit,

455
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:55,189
you don't need my help
with anything else.

456
00:21:55,190 --> 00:21:56,079
Go ahead.

457
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,270
What is it?

458
00:22:02,950 --> 00:22:04,550
My retirement insurance is up?

459
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:07,470
I can't renew it anymore?

460
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:11,360
Director,

461
00:22:11,630 --> 00:22:12,839
I...

462
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:14,750
Is this a difficult thing to tell me?

463
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,510
Didn't we agree to it?

464
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,879
As long as you can find another job,

465
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,270
just tell me.

466
00:22:21,670 --> 00:22:22,909
I will just

467
00:22:22,910 --> 00:22:24,990
close up and leave.

468
00:22:26,710 --> 00:22:28,079
Where is your next job?

469
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,319
What are the benefits?

470
00:22:29,320 --> 00:22:31,189
Do you need me to find out more?

471
00:22:31,190 --> 00:22:32,840
Do you have a better future?

472
00:22:32,990 --> 00:22:34,550
Is the employer someone ruthless?

473
00:22:35,150 --> 00:22:36,469
Don't leave a bad place

474
00:22:36,470 --> 00:22:38,310
and end up at somewhere worse.

475
00:22:38,670 --> 00:22:39,840
It's

476
00:22:40,670 --> 00:22:42,080
Ronghe Law Firm.

477
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:45,949
I have nothing to say about that.

478
00:22:45,950 --> 00:22:47,440
Have you eaten?

479
00:22:48,230 --> 00:22:49,600
You must be hungry.

480
00:22:49,990 --> 00:22:51,279
Later, let's go out

481
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:52,389
and have a farewell meal.

482
00:22:52,390 --> 00:22:53,600
How about Fried Sauce Noodles?

483
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:56,949
Fried Sauce Noodles are best
for people breaking up.

484
00:22:56,950 --> 00:22:59,200
You slurp the noodles until your mouth
is covered in black sauce.

485
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:01,470
Next, eat a few cloves of garlic.
That smell...

486
00:23:02,710 --> 00:23:04,600
You won't even feel like staying.

487
00:23:05,990 --> 00:23:07,149
Sure.

488
00:23:07,150 --> 00:23:08,440
It's my treat.

489
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:13,469
Have you prepared the materials?

490
00:23:13,470 --> 00:23:14,629
Wen Youyou's divorce case,

491
00:23:14,630 --> 00:23:17,279
Ma Jinju's inheritance dispute case,
and Xie Changting's alimony case.

492
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:18,599
The details are all here.

493
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:20,909
- Where are you two going?
- External investigation at the bank.

494
00:23:20,910 --> 00:23:22,149
A few of the parties' transactions

495
00:23:22,150 --> 00:23:23,559
need to be investigated at the bank.

496
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:25,799
Will you be passing by Huaxing Road
at around four in the evening?

497
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:27,119
I have a commissioned autopsy

498
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:28,559
at Mingjing Forensic Center.

499
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:31,030
The family members want
to have a farewell with the deceased.

500
00:23:31,230 --> 00:23:32,950
One of us needs to accompany them.

501
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:35,550
We need to go to three banks.

502
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,079
How should the route be arranged?

503
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:37,949
We'll depart now

504
00:23:37,950 --> 00:23:39,879
and avoid the congestion
at Chengdong Road.

505
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,932
We'll head to ICBC first.
Next, we'll go to CCB.

506
00:23:41,933 --> 00:23:43,253
Finally, we'll go to CMB.

507
00:23:43,360 --> 00:23:44,680
CMB?

508
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:46,429
CMB is close
to Mingjing Forensic Center.

509
00:23:46,430 --> 00:23:47,229
Let's go.

510
00:23:47,230 --> 00:23:48,440
Sure.

511
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,750
Let's go.

512
00:23:51,360 --> 00:23:52,149
Oh,

513
00:23:52,150 --> 00:23:53,519
Fan said he was going to call you.

514
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:54,359
Did he call you?

515
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,879
He did.

516
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:57,360
On which day are you going to meet him?

517
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,599
Next Tuesday.

518
00:23:58,600 --> 00:23:59,710
What time?

519
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,950
About two or three in the afternoon.

520
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:07,640
(Next Tuesday, two to three pm,
Talk to Fan about work.)

521
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:09,959
All right. I've marked it down.

522
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,839
(Judicial Appraisal Center)

523
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,189
Ms. Qin,

524
00:24:13,190 --> 00:24:14,710
you are so busy

525
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:16,879
yet you're still here to accompany me.

526
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,599
(Reception)
I'm really sorry.

527
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:19,429
Don't worry.

528
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:21,160
I'm not busy at all today.

529
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:23,230
Thank you.

530
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:43,239
(Autopsy Room)

531
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:47,560
(For Examination Purposes)

532
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:49,189
This heart is quite heavy.

533
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:50,799
It's actually 270 grams.

534
00:24:50,800 --> 00:24:52,510
It's my first time seeing
such a heavy female heart.

535
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:54,629
Her kidneys are quite heavy too.

536
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:55,599
Oh,

537
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:58,079
did you take a sample of the
lung lesion?

538
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:58,879
I did.

539
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:00,880
I took a huge sample.
It's enough for you.

540
00:25:01,950 --> 00:25:03,119
I don't want to do it.

541
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,669
I don't want to do it anymore, Ms. Qin.

542
00:25:04,670 --> 00:25:05,989
I don't want to do it.

543
00:25:05,990 --> 00:25:07,119
I don't want to do it.

544
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,669
Calm down.

545
00:25:08,670 --> 00:25:09,669
Return my father to me!

546
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:11,429
Madam Lu!

547
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:12,469
Madam Lu!

548
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:13,229
Return my father to me!

549
00:25:13,230 --> 00:25:15,079
Madam Lu!

550
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:16,360
Madam Lu!

551
00:25:18,990 --> 00:25:21,669
Madam Lu!

552
00:25:21,670 --> 00:25:22,990
Madam Lu!

553
00:25:24,390 --> 00:25:24,759
Get up.

554
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,920
What's going on?

555
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:27,079
I don't know.

556
00:25:27,080 --> 00:25:28,389
Return my father to me!

557
00:25:28,390 --> 00:25:29,629
Stand up.

558
00:25:29,630 --> 00:25:31,120
Calm down.

559
00:25:31,390 --> 00:25:35,189
Return my father to me!

560
00:25:35,190 --> 00:25:36,229
What's wrong?

561
00:25:36,230 --> 00:25:40,680
Return my father to me!

562
00:25:41,517 --> 00:25:43,629
(Judicial Appraisal Center,
Evidence Room, Medical Records Room)

563
00:25:43,630 --> 00:25:44,990
Ms. Qin,

564
00:25:45,710 --> 00:25:48,030
stop persuading me.

565
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,160
Madam Lu,

566
00:25:50,390 --> 00:25:51,879
if you refuse the autopsy,

567
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,759
the cause of your father's death
cannot be determined.

568
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:54,909
If the cause cannot be determined,

569
00:25:54,910 --> 00:25:57,440
they will insist on your fault

570
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,310
and strip your right
to inherit your father's assets.

571
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:02,990
Let them do that.

572
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,640
Let them take his assets.

573
00:26:06,470 --> 00:26:08,510
I'll give him everything.

574
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:12,750
I can't see my father being cut open

575
00:26:12,910 --> 00:26:16,310
just to get a house.

576
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,640
Aren't you letting them
bully the weak, then?

577
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,600
You work so hard

578
00:26:25,230 --> 00:26:26,550
but you still have to bear the crime.

579
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,039
Meanwhile, they did nothing

580
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:29,400
and made a lot of money.

581
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:31,839
You can't just spoil them.

582
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:34,160
No one will become
a filial child anymore.

583
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:40,360
I've caused my father's death.

584
00:26:41,390 --> 00:26:42,709
How can I

585
00:26:42,710 --> 00:26:45,950
still let him suffer after his death?

586
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:49,840
What am I doing? I'm not human.

587
00:26:54,470 --> 00:26:55,880
I don't want to do the test.

588
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:57,669
I beg you.

589
00:26:57,670 --> 00:27:00,039
I'm not doing this test anymore.

590
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:01,880
I'm really not doing it.

591
00:27:01,990 --> 00:27:04,160
I don't care how the case is decided.

592
00:27:04,670 --> 00:27:06,080
They can do whatever they want.

593
00:27:08,910 --> 00:27:10,360
Judge Shen.

594
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:15,310
I beg you.

595
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:26,360
We should still

596
00:27:26,600 --> 00:27:29,080
respect the party's intention.

597
00:27:31,630 --> 00:27:32,880
No.

598
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:36,840
Madam Lu,

599
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:38,429
if you don't want to do the autopsy,

600
00:27:38,430 --> 00:27:39,709
we won't do it.

601
00:27:39,710 --> 00:27:41,710
However, we must not surrender.

602
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,189
I think there's still a chance

603
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:45,920
regarding this case.

604
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:49,470
Slowly.

605
00:27:50,150 --> 00:27:51,400
Slowly.

606
00:27:52,230 --> 00:27:53,279
Thank you.

607
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,039
Let me carry it.

608
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:54,839
All right.

609
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:56,119
Slowly.

610
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,510
Slowly.

611
00:28:01,360 --> 00:28:01,799
Thank you.

612
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:02,950
Come on.

613
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:06,629
I've caused all of you trouble again.
Sorry.

614
00:28:06,630 --> 00:28:07,909
It's fine. It's what we should do.

615
00:28:07,910 --> 00:28:09,600
Go back and wait for an update.

616
00:28:10,910 --> 00:28:11,839
Xiang Hui,

617
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:13,429
Send Madam Lu back.

618
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:14,920
Aren't you getting in?

619
00:28:14,990 --> 00:28:16,039
I still have something to do.

620
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:17,669
I'll go back on my own later.

621
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:18,920
Sure.

622
00:28:18,950 --> 00:28:20,510
Be safe, Madam Lu.

623
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:30,559
I've been busy and haven't had
a chance to introduce you two.

624
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:32,469
This is my roommate, buddy,

625
00:28:32,470 --> 00:28:33,669
five-star chef,

626
00:28:33,670 --> 00:28:34,519
godparent,

627
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:36,440
and angel investor, Liu Lian.

628
00:28:36,990 --> 00:28:38,429
Hello.

629
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:40,229
I've heard a lot about you, Judge Shen.

630
00:28:40,230 --> 00:28:40,949
Same here.

631
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:42,182
Are you

632
00:28:42,183 --> 00:28:44,743
the fall guy
for the rearview mirror incident?

633
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:47,080
And also investor.

634
00:28:48,190 --> 00:28:50,629
Lian and I were supposed
to have a meal together.

635
00:28:50,630 --> 00:28:52,360
Why don't we eat together?

636
00:28:52,710 --> 00:28:54,469
I suddenly remember
I have something to do at night.

637
00:28:54,470 --> 00:28:55,879
Both of you should go first.

638
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:58,160
Stop finding excuses. Let's go together.

639
00:28:59,470 --> 00:29:01,149
Let's go together. It's my treat.

640
00:29:01,150 --> 00:29:03,189
There's also a dance performance later.
It's very lively.

641
00:29:03,190 --> 00:29:05,119
Will this place be too noisy?

642
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:07,080
We must raise our voices later.

643
00:29:07,670 --> 00:29:09,319
It's better than awkward silence.

644
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:10,790
Do you get it?

645
00:29:11,910 --> 00:29:13,470
It smells nice.

646
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:15,279
They even have marbled beef.

647
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,750
Let's order this.

648
00:29:17,150 --> 00:29:18,550
It looks nice.

649
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:21,519
Sorry.

650
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:22,510
Be careful.

651
00:29:26,430 --> 00:29:27,840
You scared me.

652
00:29:28,080 --> 00:29:29,470
Thankfully, you're safe.

653
00:29:30,150 --> 00:29:31,469
What do you want to eat later?

654
00:29:31,470 --> 00:29:32,640
We'll order it.

655
00:29:38,430 --> 00:29:39,840
She hit me.

656
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:42,840
Table 16 in front.

657
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:44,629
First-come, first-served.

658
00:29:44,630 --> 00:29:46,079
Both of you sit over there.

659
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:46,879
What are you doing?

660
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:48,950
I didn't say I wouldn't sit with you.

661
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:50,839
You prioritize your boyfriend over me.

662
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:52,080
What a narcissist.

663
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,669
I'll scan and order first.

664
00:29:55,670 --> 00:29:56,879
Wait.

665
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:59,119
It's my treat today.

666
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:01,229
All of you know
I'm going to Ronghe Law Firm.

667
00:30:01,230 --> 00:30:02,469
I thought

668
00:30:02,470 --> 00:30:03,709
I would be unemployed for a while

669
00:30:03,710 --> 00:30:05,279
to find a new job

670
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,680
after we got together.

671
00:30:07,040 --> 00:30:07,709
Surprisingly,

672
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:09,759
Heaven treats me well

673
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,710
and gave me a new job so soon.

674
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:15,710
First of all, today is a good day.

675
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:18,039
We are also celebrating your new job.

676
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:19,669
However, before we came here,

677
00:30:19,670 --> 00:30:21,189
I said I'd pay for this meal.

678
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,599
Both of you should stop fighting.

679
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,920
It's my treat.

680
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:28,599
Not bad, Qin Xiaorui.
You've grown up now.

681
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:30,310
I'll depend on you from now on.

682
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:31,759
I just got employed.

683
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:33,559
I'm probably just someone doing chores.

684
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:35,909
It's still a long way to go
to become a senior partner.

685
00:30:35,910 --> 00:30:38,389
After all, you are still a lawyer
who works in a popular law firm.

686
00:30:38,390 --> 00:30:40,120
Take it slow. There's no rush.

687
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:42,519
Excuse me.

688
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:44,510
Are you two a couple?

689
00:30:45,430 --> 00:30:46,079
It's like this.

690
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:47,599
There's an event in our shop.

691
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:49,669
If it's your anniversary,
you will get a 20% discount

692
00:30:49,670 --> 00:30:51,790
and a free fruit platter.

693
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:54,270
20% discount? Not bad.

694
00:30:57,390 --> 00:30:58,599
Isn't it

695
00:30:58,600 --> 00:31:00,840
your anniversary today?

696
00:31:00,950 --> 00:31:02,200
Right?

697
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:05,119
Yes. We must take advantage of this.

698
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:06,189
It's free, right?

699
00:31:06,190 --> 00:31:07,640
Sure. Sorry to trouble you.

700
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:09,320
- Thank you.
- All right. Let me get you the platter.

701
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:10,510
Thank you.

702
00:31:13,990 --> 00:31:16,440
Judge Shen is really efficient.

703
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,989
You just posted it online

704
00:31:17,990 --> 00:31:20,080
and he made it into his wallpaper today.

705
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:23,079
I finally understand what it means

706
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:25,510
to have love
is greater than everything.

707
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:26,879
But that doesn't work for me.

708
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:29,119
My love must be fed with carbohydrates.

709
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,389
Let's order. I'm starving.

710
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,469
You two may order.

711
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:33,189
You can order. What do you want to eat?

712
00:31:33,190 --> 00:31:34,510
Tomato soup.

713
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:36,120
I want Mala soup.

714
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:37,839
Waitress,

715
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:38,909
he wants mushroom soup.

716
00:31:38,910 --> 00:31:40,949
We want a pot with every soup.

717
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:42,510
We'll get everything.

718
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:43,750
Sure.

719
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:01,160
Great!

720
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:14,760
(Jiang Feng)

721
00:32:14,800 --> 00:32:16,189
(You're awesome.)

722
00:32:16,190 --> 00:32:18,030
(You fought your way out.)

723
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,920
(What's wrong?)

724
00:32:31,470 --> 00:32:33,319
(The High Court's result is out.)

725
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,840
(You've been accepted.)

726
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,600
Not bad.

727
00:32:55,910 --> 00:32:57,189
Let's take a selfie.

728
00:32:57,190 --> 00:32:58,360
Come on.

729
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:02,950
Let's take a selfie.

730
00:33:07,950 --> 00:33:09,079
It's my fault.

731
00:33:09,080 --> 00:33:10,279
I'm the only one who enjoyed it.

732
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:12,550
She has never enjoyed such performances.

733
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:15,550
Yes. I don't like these performances.

734
00:33:16,630 --> 00:33:18,030
I don't watch them.

735
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,270
What's wrong?

736
00:33:26,230 --> 00:33:27,680
Are you really upset?

737
00:33:28,150 --> 00:33:29,400
I...

738
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,440
I passed.

739
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,270
What is it?

740
00:33:40,430 --> 00:33:42,400
The high court selection result is out.

741
00:33:44,150 --> 00:33:45,750
I've been accepted.

742
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:01,990
I thought you went to Ronghe Law Firm

743
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:05,880
and I wouldn't affect you

744
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:08,560
by staying at the family court.

745
00:34:11,950 --> 00:34:13,480
But if I go to the High Court...

746
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:20,270
Let me place your pot for you.

747
00:34:20,430 --> 00:34:21,710
Thank you.

748
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:24,480
Let's drink soup.

749
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:26,430
Do you three need coriander?

750
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,480
Yes. Why not?

751
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:32,830
What about condiments?

752
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,589
We'll do it ourselves. Thank you.

753
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:36,160
Sure. The condiment bar is over there.

754
00:34:39,640 --> 00:34:41,310
I'll go and make some dipping sauce.

755
00:34:47,950 --> 00:34:49,799
Excuse me. Miss. Mister.

756
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,350
Do you have any desserts you fancy?

757
00:34:52,160 --> 00:34:55,040
Sir, why don't you help her choose one?

758
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:02,830
I don't know how to make a choice.

759
00:35:05,680 --> 00:35:06,549
These two

760
00:35:06,550 --> 00:35:07,909
are our best sellers.

761
00:35:07,910 --> 00:35:10,109
It's limited. Moreover, it's free.

762
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:11,750
Are you sure you don't want one?

763
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,389
Yes.

764
00:35:13,390 --> 00:35:15,000
Since it's limited, why not?

765
00:35:15,110 --> 00:35:16,480
I want this.

766
00:35:17,110 --> 00:35:18,350
Enjoy.

767
00:35:41,950 --> 00:35:44,040
I just made a simple sauce.

768
00:36:09,990 --> 00:36:11,390
Why aren't you eating?

769
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:14,000
The meat is cooked.

770
00:36:14,990 --> 00:36:16,639
Lian, have some meat.

771
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:18,040
Put it here first.

772
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,600
Come on.

773
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:24,480
You should eat, too.

774
00:36:28,640 --> 00:36:30,200
Eat it while it's hot. Quickly.

775
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,870
Qin Rui,

776
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:36,830
sorry.

777
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,270
Why are you apologizing?

778
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:45,160
We agreed

779
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:48,520
that this relationship is a time bomb.

780
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,750
I said

781
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,680
we could give it a try.

782
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:56,640
I just didn't expect

783
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,117
the bomb

784
00:36:58,118 --> 00:36:59,608
to go off so soon.

785
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:01,390
I know

786
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:03,230
everything I say now

787
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,230
is meaningless.

788
00:37:13,950 --> 00:37:15,270
Shen Xiezhi.

789
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:17,870
Whenever I met you back then

790
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,390
and called you by your full name,

791
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:21,040
I was either angry

792
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:23,080
or addressing you

793
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,870
as Judge Shen politely.

794
00:37:26,720 --> 00:37:27,719
I've never

795
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:29,040
called your name once.

796
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:34,560
It's a coincidence today.

797
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,870
This is a congratulations to me
for joining Ronghe Law Firm.

798
00:37:37,950 --> 00:37:39,279
I also congratulate you

799
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,750
on going to the High Court.

800
00:37:45,430 --> 00:37:46,799
After this meal,

801
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:48,200
I don't know

802
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:50,790
if we will have another chance
to meet again in the future.

803
00:37:52,390 --> 00:37:54,080
I'm using tea in place of wine
to offer you a toast.

804
00:37:54,080 --> 00:37:55,830
We must enjoy this meal.

805
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:07,239
♪Happy birthday to you♪

806
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:10,359
♪Happy birthday to you♪

807
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:13,750
♪Happy birthday to you♪

808
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:17,069
♪Happy birthday to you♪

809
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:19,390
Happy birthday!

810
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:25,759
♪When a leaf can't find a place to fall♪

811
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,270
Eat. Don't space out.

812
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,600
Add more meat in.

813
00:38:29,730 --> 00:38:33,020
♪Wandering without a destination♪

814
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,239
The vegetable is cooked.

815
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:35,549
Here. Eat more.

816
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:41,100
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

817
00:38:42,250 --> 00:38:43,809
♪I've decided♪

818
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:47,160
♪To stay by your side♪

819
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:54,330
♪Become your soaring wings♪

820
00:38:55,720 --> 00:39:02,720
♪Let me be your safe haven♪

821
00:39:03,130 --> 00:39:06,759
♪I want to be in your world♪

822
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:10,259
♪And cast away my disguise♪

823
00:39:10,260 --> 00:39:16,279
♪Lean on my tender shoulder♪

824
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:19,120
(Grandfather)

825
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,319
Xiezhi,

826
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,910
when are you coming back?

827
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:24,069
My screen turned black

828
00:39:24,070 --> 00:39:25,830
when I was halfway done
writing that thing.

829
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:32,350
Grandpa, don't touch the computer first.

830
00:39:32,470 --> 00:39:33,830
I'll be there in half an hour.

831
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:37,279
Excuse me,

832
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,549
please turn around
and head to Yunshui Garden.

833
00:39:39,550 --> 00:39:40,680
Sure.

834
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:51,620
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

835
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:54,389
♪I've decided♪

836
00:39:54,390 --> 00:39:57,690
♪To stay by your side♪

837
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:04,990
♪Become your soaring wings♪

838
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,799
What are you doing?

839
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,270
You can't drink.

840
00:40:13,630 --> 00:40:17,249
♪I want to be in your world♪

841
00:40:17,250 --> 00:40:20,879
♪And cast away my disguise♪

842
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:27,530
♪Lean on my tender shoulder♪

843
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:31,379
♪I want to be in your world♪

844
00:40:31,380 --> 00:40:34,969
♪I'll be your shelter♪

845
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:41,880
♪I'll be there for you
until the very end♪

846
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:45,529
♪I want to be in your world♪

847
00:40:45,530 --> 00:40:49,139
♪And forget the passage of time♪

848
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:55,970
♪You are the only one that I see♪

849
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:59,689
♪I want to be in your world♪

850
00:40:59,690 --> 00:41:03,239
♪Everything is no longer faraway♪

851
00:41:03,240 --> 00:41:09,930
♪I'll be there for you
until the very end♪

852
00:41:46,550 --> 00:41:47,790
Xiezhi,

853
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,120
you're back.

854
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:52,350
Yes.

855
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:54,080
Grandpa's computer is broken.

856
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,389
I came back to fix his computer.

857
00:41:55,390 --> 00:41:56,359
Let me ask you.

858
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,879
When we meet your girlfriend tomorrow,

859
00:41:57,880 --> 00:41:59,199
should we give her a red envelope

860
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:00,870
or buy accessories for her?

861
00:42:02,910 --> 00:42:04,480
Let me fix Grandpa's computer first.

862
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:06,159
Forget about the computer.

863
00:42:06,160 --> 00:42:07,679
Where is your girlfriend from?

864
00:42:07,680 --> 00:42:09,350
Let's go out and eat tomorrow.

865
00:42:09,550 --> 00:42:11,160
What does she like to eat?

866
00:42:12,950 --> 00:42:14,350
Forget about it.

867
00:42:14,990 --> 00:42:16,870
Why not?

868
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:17,719
It's our first meeting.

869
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:19,750
We must give her a good impression.

870
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:21,430
We broke up.

871
00:42:23,430 --> 00:42:23,719
What...

872
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:25,040
Oh.

873
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,910
I've been accepted by the High Court.

874
00:42:27,950 --> 00:42:29,480
After a while,

875
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:31,640
I have to go and report for duty.

876
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:48,390
This is the WeChat chat history

877
00:42:49,030 --> 00:42:51,430
(Chat History with Brother)
between the plaintiff and my defendant.

878
00:42:52,910 --> 00:42:56,910
The deposit will be paid
with our father's retirement fund.

879
00:42:56,950 --> 00:42:59,159
I heard
it was a fierce argument in the past.

880
00:42:59,160 --> 00:43:01,520
I thought you were the one
who paid for it.

881
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:03,750
Turns out
the money is still your father's.

882
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

883
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

884
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

885
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

886
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

887
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

888
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

889
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

890
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

891
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

892
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

893
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

894
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

895
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

896
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

897
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

898
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

899
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

900
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

901
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

902
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

903
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

904
